{"tid":1567232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"831死亡人仕","createTime":"2019-09-14T03:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T15:25:55.000Z","uid":178726,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e50bcbe5d4bf74c0dd468aab88ce2636b4df262b","tid":1567232,"uid":178726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:44:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;代朋友轉貼&gt;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n本人廢中一名，苦覓連登朋友不果，希望有心人可轉發<br />\n(以下係家人親身經歷)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一位超高靈，但冇任何法力人仕平凡人，在今日（12/9）喺太子站「見」到嘅女亡靈，頭部大量流血😭<br />\n以下資料<br />\n<br />\n亡者：陳泳霖(或同音)<br />\n約19歲，約高168cm,<br />\n瘦身材(約110磅)，長直髮齊蔭，大眼睛<br />\n住大埔，<br />\n讀天主教學校或信仰係天主教(因只聽到「天主教」尼3個字<br />\n<br />\n事發時穿黑衫，戴黑幼框眼鏡，藍色運動褲，黑色Reebok,黑色腰包<br />\n<br />\n如各位認識尼個名字，請確認831後是否尚在，吾排除好多同名同姓，確認左尚在可安心，假若真係失蹤，定必要為亡者討回公道<br />\n<br />\n2019年9月12日"},{"pid":"fe80f319172d04b66212ca2106c809c5a1228c10","tid":1567232,"uid":56063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1fc61d9e3a9f4659cc9ab8e62121919d24ce8a","tid":1567232,"uid":135067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未FACTCHECK唔推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g